{"tid":2233853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Jack】斯洛伐克總統拒演講後 當地安全論壇解除華為贊助關係","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:27:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cfa5582b0b58c02bfea5fe2f69397b74a6180f","tid":2233853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"中國電訊設備巨頭華為，在西方再遇抵制。外電報道，北約成員國斯洛伐克的總統查普托娃（Zuzana Caputova），拒絕在當地一個安全論壇上發表講話後，論壇主辦單位與華為解除贊助關係。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社形容，這對美國來說是一場勝利。美國一直遊說盟友封殺華為，禁止華為參與5G網絡等科技項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2771136/1007014_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2771136%2F1007014_600.jpg&h=9139ef45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 斯洛伐克總統查普托娃（右）<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，查普托娃原計劃周三（7日）在智庫Globsec的一個論壇上發表講話，但她一度取消。隨後Globsec與華為解除贊助關係，她又恢復原先的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n查普托娃的發言人Martin Strizinec表示，查普托娃認為，「在贊助商包括這樣一家公司的會議上發表講話，是一個不好的信號」，稱對她來說不只是安全問題，也是原則和價值觀的問題。<br />\n<br />\nGlobsec在聲明強調，無論是華為還是其他合作夥伴，都不會對論壇或研究的內容產生任何影響。華為斯洛伐克分公司未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://china.hket.com/article/2771136</code></pre>"},{"pid":"10eb098cc00e07d40c82930d5acfcca57d4c9b91","tid":2233853,"uid":128102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"dllm<br />\n全球杯葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105348ec09c08261b5f98a0a529b7f61edffd8b5","tid":2233853,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"撚狗"},{"pid":"a3be631a06667173f87365d5e66e3f258022f4cf","tid":2233853,"uid":59511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"Jack slow fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdb71db2cc826a0440e06ad903e52a0b956726c","tid":2233853,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedB